#
# how to set Underline / Bold / Italic in notepad++ v6.7.9.2
#
goto menu -> Settings -> Preferences -> Style Configurator
	Select theme:	Default(stylers.xml)
	Language:	Global Styles ( or other language same as the file )
	Style:		ex. Default Style
		=>	Font Style: tickle Underline / Bold / Italic
		
# ref doc:	http://www.groovypost.com/howto/notepad-plus-plus-change-font-color/
